# eq-reflexive

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `boolean_simplification_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (eq ?x ?x)
rhs: (const-bool true)
